description: Between the sun and these four beautiful bodies, there's enough heat outside to melt the asphalt. Thankfully, relief is just a splish splash away, as these guys soak down the ride before heading inside to heat up again. Princeton Price and Johnny B are both ready for a good hard fucking, and Jet Davis and Mathias are just the studs to give it to them. The car isn't the only thing getting hosed down, but before the final splash, there's plenty of wet and wild action to go around for everyone.Enjoy!
series: NDB - 5033 - Mathias, Johnny B, Princeton Price & Jet Davis
title: Soaking Wet
